{"data":[{"date":"07:04 30/07","title":"Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/ronaldo-tro-lai-juventus-tap-luyen-cung-dong-doi.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110TQG v\u00e0 gi\u1edd m\u1edbi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Turin.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Juventus</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 4 t\u1ea1i Real Madrid v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 5 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a qua, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd chia tay CLB. Sau nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 thu\u1ebf v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t Juventus b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi Ronaldo. H\u1ecd g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro (88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) t\u1edbi Real v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y minh ch\u1ee9ng cho tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Cristiano-Ronaldo-tro-lai-Juventus-tap-luyen-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u&nbsp;Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n7 n\u0103m qua, Juventus \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A song kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Bianconeri l\u00e0 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i vinh quang \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u sau 22 n\u0103m v\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c chinh ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u00f4m qua, Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8. H\u1eadu World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p th\u00eam ng\u00e0y ph\u00e9p v\u00e0 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"cristiano ronaldo\" title=\"cristiano ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/cristiano-ronaldo.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 c\u1edd hoa. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Benfica, cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u kh\u1ea3 quan t\u1eeb d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 v\u1edbi C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 MLS v\u00e0 Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Ronaldo, m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u1ee7a Juventus c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng Paulo Dybala, Douglas Costa, Rodrigo Bentancur, Mario Mandzukic, Marko Pjaca, Blaise Matuidi v\u00e0 Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong phi\u00ean t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u00f4m nay c\u1ee7a Juventus. Tuy nhi\u00ean, bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf c\u1eeda cho c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-ban-3-cau-thu-mua-pogba-172-192247.html\">Juventus b\u00e1n 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mua sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-chieu-mo-sao-juventus-172-192204.html\">Pep Guardiola l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bld-mu-ngan-can-mourinho-chieu-mo-sandro-172-192120.html\">BL\u0110 MU ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Mourinho chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/xac-dinh-doi-thu-dau-tien-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-tren-dat-y-176-192108.html\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u00dd</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1787","checkdouble":"192282"},{"date":"07:31 30/07","title":"Chelsea s\u1eafp v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/chelsea-sap-vo-mong-chieu-mo-tuyen-thu-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton. T\u1edd Sunday Times \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 Bayern Munich.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pickford tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &ldquo;h\u00e0ng hot&rdquo;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, Jordan Pickford b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd khi m\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ef1 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. Anh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc trong khung th\u00e0nh Tam s\u01b0, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua Croatia trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau World Cup, Pickford nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Nh\u1eefng Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Everton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Jordan-Pickford-sap-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-Everton-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pickford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u sau World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Chelsea khi h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm g\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thay th\u1ebf Thibaut Courtois. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ee5c r\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 trong m\u01a1 Real Madrid.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Sunday Times m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 Bayern v\u00e0 Chelsea bu\u1ed3n l\u00f2ng. Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc 1 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"jordan pickford\" title=\"jordan pickford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/jordan-pickford-cua-Everton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u01b0ng Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Everton b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Pickford t\u1eeb Sunderland. Th\u1eddi gian tr\u00f4i qua, gi\u1edd h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m m\u1edbi giao k\u00e8o v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n, Everton c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n gia t\u0103ng m\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Pickford v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018. Sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, anh s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng Everton tham gia v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League v\u1edbi Wolves ng\u00e0y 11/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain-172-192257.html\">Chelsea chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Higuain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/drinkwater-muon-roi-chelsea-o-he-2018-172-192252.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c Stamford Bridge</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-olivier-giroud-172-192243.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua Olivier Giroud</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/chelsea-bat-ngo-muon-so-huu-ngoi-sao-cua-arsenal-187-192241.html\">Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1786","checkdouble":"192283"},{"date":"07:58 30/07","title":"Mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201csao x\u1ecbt\u201d World Cup, M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/22/hlv-kovac-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-lewandowski-roi-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 30/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern: PSG ch\u01b0a h\u1ecfi mua Boateng. </strong>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern Munich, Karl-Heinz Rummenigge kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb Paris Saint-Germain. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n PSG nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c thay th\u1ebf l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Thiago Silva. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 M.U.</strong> Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Aurelio De Laurentiis cho bi\u1ebft Napoli \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1edbi Manchester United cho tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Matteo Darmian. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n sau 2 n\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3ng vai d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 307 L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 307 L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/30/sao-mu-chinh-thuc-duoc-hoi-mua-boi-napoli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Napoli \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201csao x\u1ecbt\u201d World Cup, M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. </strong>M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Lewandowski. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan mu\u1ed1n l\u0129nh kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng thua nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Alexis Sanchez \u0111ang nh\u1eadn t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Chelsea s\u1eafp v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh. </strong>Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton. T\u1edd Sunday Times \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Simeone thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Vrsaljko \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico. </strong>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Sime Vrsaljko \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Inter Milan ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n. HLV Diego Simeone hy v\u1ecdng tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sime Vrsaljko\" title=\"Sime Vrsaljko\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/17/sao-atletico-madrid-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-khoac-ao-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Vrsaljko trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Atletico</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 sao tr\u1ebb ra \u0111i. </strong>Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 3,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Rosenborg cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pedro Chirivella. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 m\u1edbi g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HLV Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Bale.</strong> Mauricio Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1c b\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gareth Bale tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Tottenham t\u1eeb Real Madrid. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina cho hay Spurs kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng r\u1ea5t cao t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>CLB h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch mua Ojo c\u1ee7a Liverpool. </strong>Middlesbrough \u0111ang m\u1edf nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Sheyi Ojo t\u1eeb Liverpool. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho Fulham m\u01b0\u1ee3n nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t. Ngo\u00e0i Boro, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Nottingham Forest c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd Ojo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1785","checkdouble":"192284"},{"date":"08:16 30/07","title":"MU c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/mu-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-harry-maguire.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Don Balon \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Maguire l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, M.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. HLV Jose Mourinho r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Eric Bailly \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Vuot-mat-MU,-Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Harry-Maguire-hinh-anh.jpg\"><br>\r\n            \u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Maguire \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leicester, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh. Maguire s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh ghi t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-utd-san-sang-pha-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong-de-chieu-mo-ngoi-sao-tuyen-anh-172-192100.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Maguire</span>, h\u1ecd \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Maguire</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Don Balon \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"MU c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/MU-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-muc-tieu-65-trieu-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Harry Maguire</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda Leicester, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Sergio Ramos. Los Blancos c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra t\u1eeb 60 \u0111\u1ebfn 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi m\u1ea5t Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay Juventus, Real \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Khi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Neymar, Mbappe hay Eden Hazard \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3, n\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Maguire th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho c\u1ea3 M.U v\u00e0 Real Madrid l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 Leicester \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n King Power \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ho\u1eb7c Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ti\u1ec1n, Maguire s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Van Dijk \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1784","checkdouble":"192285"},{"date":"08:31 30/07","title":"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Sao Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 99%, twitter c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eafp t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lucas Digne mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLucas Digne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Alba, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca. 2 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Xac-nhan-Lucas-Digne-roi-Barca-cap-ben-Everton-voi-gia-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Lucas Digne mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Digne kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb HLV Ernesto Valverde, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 8 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf La Liga. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, Lucas Digne \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Barca c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1993, song vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Barca y\u00eau c\u1ea7u khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Sau \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Lucas Digne</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Digne, trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca xac nhan Digne cap ben Everton\" title=\"Barca x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Digne c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Digne s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/lucas-digne-chuan-bi-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191654.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton </span>\u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 99%, twitter c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eafp t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia v\u00e0 Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Digne v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 xin ph\u00e9p Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDigne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd bay t\u1edbi Anh v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 3 tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 4. \u1ede s\u00e2n Goodison Park, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Leighton Baines.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Digne s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Everton d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Marco Silva, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Richarlison t\u1eeb Watford. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng chia tay Wayne Rooney v\u00e0 Ramiro Funes Mori.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1783","checkdouble":"192286"},{"date":"08:07 30/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 30/7: L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/30/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-307-lo-dien-ben-do-bat-ngo-cua-hau-ve-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 30/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern: PSG ch\u01b0a h\u1ecfi mua Boateng. </strong>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern Munich, Karl-Heinz Rummenigge kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb Paris Saint-Germain. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n PSG nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c thay th\u1ebf l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Thiago Silva. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 M.U.</strong> Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Aurelio De Laurentiis cho bi\u1ebft Napoli \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1edbi Manchester United cho tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Matteo Darmian. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n sau 2 n\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3ng vai d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 307 L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 307 L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/30/sao-mu-chinh-thuc-duoc-hoi-mua-boi-napoli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Napoli \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201csao x\u1ecbt\u201d World Cup, M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. </strong>M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Lewandowski. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan mu\u1ed1n l\u0129nh kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng thua nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Alexis Sanchez \u0111ang nh\u1eadn t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Chelsea s\u1eafp v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh. </strong>Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton. T\u1edd Sunday Times \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Simeone thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Vrsaljko \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico. </strong>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Sime Vrsaljko \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Inter Milan ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n. HLV Diego Simeone hy v\u1ecdng tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sime Vrsaljko\" title=\"Sime Vrsaljko\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/17/sao-atletico-madrid-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-khoac-ao-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Vrsaljko trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Atletico</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 sao tr\u1ebb ra \u0111i. </strong>Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 3,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Rosenborg cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pedro Chirivella. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 m\u1edbi g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HLV Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Bale.</strong> Mauricio Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1c b\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gareth Bale tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Tottenham t\u1eeb Real Madrid. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina cho hay Spurs kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng r\u1ea5t cao t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>CLB h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch mua Ojo c\u1ee7a Liverpool. </strong>Middlesbrough \u0111ang m\u1edf nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Sheyi Ojo t\u1eeb Liverpool. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho Fulham m\u01b0\u1ee3n nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t. Ngo\u00e0i Boro, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Nottingham Forest c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd Ojo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1782","checkdouble":"192287"},{"date":"08:33 30/07","title":"HLV Kovac l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Lewandowski r\u1eddi Bayern","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/22/hlv-kovac-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-lewandowski-roi-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Niko Kovac kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Lewandowski s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Bayern m\u1eb7c cho nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1eafn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c.</h2><h2>Lewandowski \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Bayern</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Lewandowski l\u00e0 Pini Zahavi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Allianz Arena. V\u00e0 HLV Kovac c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft mong mu\u1ed1n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Lewandowski \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian. V\u00e0 sau khi Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Bernabeu, c\u00e1i t\u00ean Lewandowski l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecfa l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Real b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCEO Hans-Joachim Watzke c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed5 th\u00eam d\u1ea7u v\u00e0o l\u1eeda khi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf ra 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Lewandowski tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 x\u01b0a.</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Kovac b\u00e1c b\u1ecf tin \u0111\u1ed3n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Kovac ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn tin \u0111\u1ed3n Lewandowski r\u1eddi Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Kovac ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn tin \u0111\u1ed3n Lewandowski r\u1eddi Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/hlv-kovac-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-lewandowski-roi-bayern.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV&nbsp;Kovac ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn tin \u0111\u1ed3n Lewandowski r\u1eddi Bayern</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n tr\u00ean b\u00e1o ch\u00ed cho th\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-duc/4-diem-den-ly-tuong-neu-lewandowski-roi-bayern-munich-193-187814.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lewandowski r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Bayern</span> kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xa. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Kovac ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec m\u1edbi x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Lewandowski. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Bayern v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tu\u1ed9t kh\u1ecfi tay m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f9ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Lewandowski l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ea1i Bundesliga. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 Lewandowski c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00edch kh\u00f4ng tr\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u00edch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Lewandowski c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 l\u00e0 bao l\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern l\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Bayern:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-23-man-city-icc-2018-329-192238.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Bayern Munich 2-3 Man City (ICC 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tan-hlv-bayern-munich-nguong-mo-nguoi-cu-pep-guardiola-184-192215.html\">T\u00e2n HLV Bayern Munich ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Pep Guardiola</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1781","checkdouble":"192288"},{"date":"08:52 30/07","title":"David Luiz mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, ph\u00f2 t\u00e1 Sarri","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/david-luiz-mong-muon-o-lai-chelsea-pho-ta-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 David Luiz kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u1eabn h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri.</h2><h2>David Luiz h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, David Luiz \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1eeda \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1ee1 quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi HLV Conte v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAnh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 17 tr\u1eadn m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Conte ra \u0111i, David Luiz \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea. HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u00e3 qua. Luiz thi \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 anh c\u0169ng m\u1edbi b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Sarri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Luiz mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, ph\u00f2 t\u00e1 Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Luiz mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, ph\u00f2 t\u00e1 Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/david-luiz-mong-muon-o-lai-chelsea-pho-ta-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>David Luiz mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, ph\u00f2 t\u00e1 Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. Khi t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb Paris, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f9ng Chelsea. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i y\u00eau tri\u1ebft l\u00fd m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u00e2ng cao, c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u. HLV Sarri lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Luiz \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o Jorginho</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 k\u00edch n\u1ed5 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d mang t\u00ean Jorginho v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang ch\u1ee9ng minh r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh The Blues. V\u00e0 David Luiz tin r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd g\u1ed1c Brazil n\u00e0y th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cJorginho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Jorginho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng, lu\u00f4n \u1edf nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng h\u01b0\u1edbng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-sap-vo-mong-chieu-mo-tuyen-thu-anh-172-192283.html\">Chelsea s\u1eafp v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain-172-192257.html\">Chelsea chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Higuain</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1780","checkdouble":"192289"},{"date":"08:50 30/07","title":"T\u1eeb b\u1ecf Hazard, Real mu\u1ed1n chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/tu-bo-hazard-real-muon-chi-100-trieu-bang-cho-courtois-va-willian.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 t\u00ednh chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 Willian, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal nh\u1eafm Eden Hazard nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991, song r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois v\u00e0 Willian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois v\u00e0 Willian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-muon-mua-Courtois-va-Willian-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Hazard, n\u1ebfu Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Neymar \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Los Blancos kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed theo AS, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-khong-muon-mua-hazard-180-192194.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real t\u1eeb b\u1ecf vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Hazard</span>. Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Lopetegui s\u1ebd x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Los Blancos quanh Isco thay v\u00ec chi m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u00f4i v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea c\u00e0ng cao, The Blues v\u1eabn \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Courtois v\u00e0 Willian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 t\u00ednh chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 Willian, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Thay v\u00ec mua Hazard th\u00ec Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real tinh chi 100 trieu bang mua Courtois va Willian\" title=\"Real t\u00ednh chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Courtois v\u00e0 Willian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/tu-bo-hazard-real-muon-chi-100-trieu-bang-cho-courtois-va-willian.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real t\u00ednh chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Courtois v\u00e0 Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCourtois \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, n\u1ebfu The Blues kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Courtois cho Real v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Sau khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c mua Willian. Chelsea \u0111\u00f2i 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n MU c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian, song ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Chelsea \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho Los Blancos h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u00e0 Willian, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Real s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1779","checkdouble":"192290"},{"date":"08:53 30/07","title":"HLV Toshiya Miura tin \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u00f4m h\u1eadn","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/22/hlv-toshiya-miura-noi-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ed9i U21 d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, HLV Toshiya Miura \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n x\u1ee9 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Olympic 2020 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, L\u0110B\u0110 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb r\u00e8n gi\u0169a, t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam kinh nghi\u1ec7m thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf ASIAD n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/22/hlv-toshiya-miura-noi-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 mang tuy\u1ebfn tr\u1ebb U21 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y su\u1ea5t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D l\u00e0 Nepal v\u00e0 Pakistan \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Toshiya Miura cho r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D: \"Theo t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft th\u00ec Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 mang l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U21 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i. N\u1ebfu gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, HLV Miura c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u1ea3 quan khi gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup 2017, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb, HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: \"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng gi\u00fap h\u1ecd t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Miura t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng U23 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft CLB TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh, hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 11 trong b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng V-League 2018.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-u23-viet-nam-lai-duoc-vinh-danh-tren-bao-nuoc-ngoai-168-192270.html\">\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh tr\u00ean b\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-hoc-lom-bai-tu-cua-nguoi-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-168-192269.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u201ch\u1ecdc l\u1ecfm b\u00e0i t\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tu-tin-se-duoc-thay-park-giu-lai-168-192239.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-dau-tien-168-192236.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/duc-chinh-hoan-thien-ban-than-nho-thay-park-thich-da-cap-voi-cong-phuong-168-192232.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n nh\u1edd th\u1ea7y Park, th\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-truot-bai-kiem-tra-the-luc-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-192230.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1778","checkdouble":"192292"},{"date":"21:48 29/07","title":"\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh tr\u00ean b\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/dt-u23-viet-nam-lai-duoc-vinh-danh-tren-bao-nuoc-ngoai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd FOX Sports m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft cho r\u1eb1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia n\u00ean l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh tr\u00ean b\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh tr\u00ean b\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh tr\u00ean b\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-giai-tu-hung-vff-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>FOX Sports cho r\u1eb1ng Indonesia c\u1ea7n h\u1ecdc theo \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i FOX Sports m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 t\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Indonesia c\u1ea7n l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb\u00a0nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf\u00a0n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">FOX Sports vi\u1ebft: \"Ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Indonesia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n v\u1ebd l\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i ASIAD\u2026 \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2u \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi ch\u00e2u \u00c1, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Indonesia \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf ASIAD 18. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng hay kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn c\u00e0ng s\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 l\u1edbn lao c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Indonesia, \u0111\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Indonesia s\u1ebd c\u1ea5t c\u00e1nh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y trong th\u00e1ng 1 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Trung Qu\u1ed1c. Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Tr\u00ean su\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp khi c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Indonesia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f4ng d\u00e2n h\u01a1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Indonesia t\u00e1i l\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch nh\u01b0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng\u2026\u201d. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 c\u00f9ng L\u00e0o, Hong Kong, \u0110\u00e0i Loan v\u00e0 Palestine. N\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f9ng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng V\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-hoc-lom-bai-tu-cua-nguoi-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-168-192269.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-hoc-lom-bai-tu-cua-nguoi-anh-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-hoc-lom-bai-tu-cua-nguoi-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-168-192269.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u201ch\u1ecdc l\u1ecfm b\u00e0i t\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng \u0111ang cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1777","checkdouble":"192270"},{"date":"22:08 29/07","title":"B\u1ea1n th\u00e2n Neymar mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ea1i Spurs","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/19/ban-than-neymar-muon-lam-nen-lich-su-tai-spurs.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi Premier League, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Lucas Moura h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Tottenham, qua nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMoura quy\u1ebft l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i l\u00e0m quen tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i PSG (v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u00fd do b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Neymar), ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Lucas Moura \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. Anh \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Tottenham v\u00e0o k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Khi t\u00f4i c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Brazil, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n sang ch\u00e2u \u00c2u thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y. T\u1ea1i Brazil, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1ea1o l\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Moura h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Tottenham\" title=\"Lucas Moura cua Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/2/Truoc-vong-26-Premier-League-Man-chao-hang-cua-bom-tan-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lucas Moura h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i l\u1edbn l\u00ean \u1edf m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t ngh\u00e8o. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n t\u00e2m ni\u1ec7m ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Premier League, Champions League. \u0110\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi t\u1eeb Ch\u00faa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ea1i Tottenham. \u0110\u00e2t l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi chuy\u1ec3n sang Spurs. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u, gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;6 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi, l\u00e0m qu\u00ean v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&rdquo; &ndash; Lucas Moura h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-gap-kho-vu-mua-grealish-172-192258.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/tottenham-gap-kho-vu-mua-grealish.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-gap-kho-vu-mua-grealish-172-192258.html\">Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua sao h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t</span><br>\r\nTottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua Grealish. CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Aston Villa c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi sau khi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong b\u00e0i to\u00e1n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea</span><br>\r\nWilfried Zaha n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Crystal Palace \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-barca-22-pen-53-tottenham-icc-2018-329-192246.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/video-tong-hop-barca-22-pen-53-tottenham-icc-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-barca-22-pen-53-tottenham-icc-2018-329-192246.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Barca 2-2 (pen 5-3) Tottenham (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London san b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau khi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 La Masia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1776","checkdouble":"192271"},{"date":"22:22 29/07","title":"Pochettino kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua l\u1ea1i Gareth Bale","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/27/pochettino-khang-dinh-khong-mua-lai-gareth-bale.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Aurelio De Laurentiis x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Napoli h\u1ecfi mua Darmian \u2013 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Man United.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nNapoli li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Darmian<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Italia, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Matteo Darmian d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf Old Trafford. Ch\u00ednh anh c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t sau khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb cho ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Man United.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Serie A \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y, g\u1ed3m Juventus, Inter Milan v\u00e0 Napoli. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Naples \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Darmian.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t. Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu M.U kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 6 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c. Trong \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Benjamin Henrichs t\u1eeb Bayer Leverkusen, ho\u1eb7c Santiago Arias c\u1ee7a PSV.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\" Napoli h\u1ecfi mua Darmian c\u1ee7a M.U\" title=\"Darmian cua MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/ngay-hom-nay-127.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Napoli h\u1ecfi mua Darmian c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3n Darmian ra \u0111i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd &ndash; \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi ch\u00ednh h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Italia, anh c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. B\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng, anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, Man United \u0111ang kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Antonio Valencia v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Premier League. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda t\u00e2n binh Diogo Dalot, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u1ea3 d\u0129 kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao ni\u1ec1m tin, ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Ashley Young v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Victor Lindelof. D\u00f9 sao, Mourinho c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb Napoli h\u1ecfi mua Darmian, n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mac-mourinho-can-vien-doi-truong-mu-quyet-tam-ra-di-172-192213.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/mac-mourinho-can-vien-doi-truong-mu-quyet-tam-ra-di.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mac-mourinho-can-vien-doi-truong-mu-quyet-tam-ra-di-172-192213.html\">M\u1eb7c Mourinho c\u1ea7u vi\u1ec7n, &ldquo;\u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng&rdquo; MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i</span><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Matteo Darmian l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mong mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i ngay trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/valencia-dinh-chan-thuong-mu-khung-hoang-hau-ve-phai-172-192097.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/valencia-dinh-chan-thuong-mu-khung-hoang-hau-ve-phai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/valencia-dinh-chan-thuong-mu-khung-hoang-hau-ve-phai-172-192097.html\">Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, M.U kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf - h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Antonio Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y Premier League kh\u1edfi tranh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1775","checkdouble":"192272"},{"date":"22:43 29/07","title":"Neymar s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/neymar-se-som-tro-lai-sau-tham-hoa-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng PSG \u2013 HLV Tuchel chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Neymar v\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nTuchel kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Neymar s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1eabn trong th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau khi tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y vui v\u1ebb, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, HLV Thomas Tuchel cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Neymar c\u1ea7n th\u00eam b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c n\u00e0o so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Brazil mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap Neymar tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u1ebft m\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;B\u1ecf qua s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Neymar s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i \u0111au th\u00e0nh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. B\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch trong th\u1ec3 thao, v\u00e0 Neymar s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tuchel chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi\" title=\"Neymar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/neymar-se-som-tro-lai-sau-tham-hoa-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Tuchel chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Ph\u00e1p, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 26 b\u00e0n sau 29 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Ligue 1. Anh g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 2, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng Selecao khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 PSG sau nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, b\u1ecf ngo\u00e0i tai nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Neymar s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia m\u1edbi. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00e2n HLV Tuchel chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Neymar, anh \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va-197-191719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/12/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va-197-191719.html\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u0169 kh\u00f4ng n\u00e3o m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Neymar</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ea5u m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil t\u1ea1o ra t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t leo thang, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dani Alves l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien-421-190281.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien-421-190281.html\">Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean t\u1eeb b\u1ecf nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ngh\u1ec1 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Mexico 2-0, ng\u00f4i sao Brazil \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1774","checkdouble":"192273"},{"date":"23:01 29/07","title":"V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Morata ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eb7p song sinh c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1ng y\u00eau","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/vo-chong-morata-chao-don-cap-song-sinh-cuc-dang-yeu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea \u2013 Alvaro Morata ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eb7p song sinh Alessandro v\u00e0 Leonardo.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMorata l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap n\u01a1i h\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 vui m\u1eebng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram, v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n 2 ch\u00fa nh\u00f3c xinh x\u1eafn v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt (gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alvaro Morata cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;V\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn &ndash; 29/7/2018, m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qu\u00ean. Kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 d\u00e0i. D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 9 th\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 3 n\u0103m. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1eddi n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n t\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft \u01a1n v\u1edbi Alice, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n em v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 trao cho anh m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u00f4i ng\u00e0y k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi quen em, anh lu\u00f4n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ta \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi nhau, em l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a anh. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, em \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t con s\u01b0 t\u1eed c\u00e1i, v\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00eam trong b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng nhau r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Morata ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eb7p song sinh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/vo-chong-morata-chao-don-cap-song-sinh-cuc-dang-yeu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Morata ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eb7p song sinh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng 2 con \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5t n\u00e0y, Alessandro v\u00e0 Leonardo. Cha ch\u1ec9 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c con s\u1ebd th\u1eadt kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n t\u00ecnh y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00edt th\u1edf b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong c\u0103n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta, m\u00e1i \u1ea5m c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u1ea3i qua kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n Angelo. Xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n l\u00f2ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi!&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng xem nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Alvaro Morata ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eb7p song sinh<br>\r\n</strong> <br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/alice.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alice \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/morata.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata vui m\u1eebng ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n 2 thi\u00ean th\u1ea7n nh\u1ecf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chua-co-bom-tan-hlv-sarri-van-hy-vong-bom-xit-morata-toa-sang-172-192227.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/chua-co-bom-tan-hlv-sarri-van-hy-vong-bom-xit-morata-toa-sang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chua-co-bom-tan-hlv-sarri-van-hy-vong-bom-xit-morata-toa-sang-172-192227.html\">Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 bom t\u1ea5n, HLV Sarri v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng bom x\u1ecbt Morata t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng</span><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, HLV Sarri hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Morata s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain-172-192257.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain-172-192257.html\">Chelsea chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Higuain</span><br>\r\nChelsea d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Higuain. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc AC Milan d\u00f9 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Juventus.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1773","checkdouble":"192274"}]}